安装ruby-oci8
----------------------------------------------------



```
$ gem install ruby-oci8
sudo yum install ruby-devel
```


Quick Start
------------------------------------------------------

```
$ ruby -r oci8 -e "OCI8.new('apple', '111111').exec('select * from t') do |r| puts r.join(','); end"
Warning: NLS_LANG is not set. fallback to US7ASCII.
0.1E1,0.1E1
0.1E1,0.1E1
0.1E1,0.1E1
0.1E1,0.1E1
0.1E1,0.1E1
0.1E1,0.1E1
```


